Talaria of Magic.lore:
Sandals forged eons ago,
for a speedster that never ran,
for a merchant that never sold.

Queen's Crown.lore:
Isadora looked up at the sky above;
the rain hid the tears rolling down her face.
She would never forgive the one who killed him.

